          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Collaborations -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>Collaborations</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://www.torproject.org/">Tor Project</a> &mdash;
        Weekly collaboration on embedding <a href="https://gitlab.torproject.org/tpo/core/arti">Arti</a> in the browser via WASM, with the goal of merging our changes into upstream Arti.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://hackmd.io/@turanzv/S1G3vMPXbl">Turan</a> &mdash;
        Micro-grant recipient working on a <a href="https://efdn.notion.site/PAPs-0cbd98955541825296e201936c5361f2">PAP-2.1</a> PIR scheme specification and reference implementation.
      </p>
      <p class="collab-cta">
        <em>
          If you work on privacy research or tools that
          <a href="https://blog.ethereum.org/2026/03/13/ef-mandate">align</a> with
          <a href={`${base}/workstreams`}>our work</a> and approach, please reach out outlining your proposal of collaboration.
        </em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Team */
  .team-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .team-member {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .team-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .team-member h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .team-role {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .team-role::before {
    content: '/';
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .team-icons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-left: 0.25rem;
  }
  .team-icons a {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    transition: color 0.2s var(--ease);
    display: flex;
  }
  .team-icons a:hover { color: var(--text); }

  /* Collaborations */
  .collab-cta {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .team-member {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }
  }
</style>
